{"tid":1924953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林本利 : 兩元任搭　由年輕人埋單","createTime":"2020-03-14T04:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T05:42:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1841fcedd6fff5060f65c59db0af53f4cf75f86","tid":1924953,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/MwQCwtWUdpAmgk6RtnLKUZnfJEY=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/QTSNVWO3556NRZAIY5JCTPUIRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FMwQCwtWUdpAmgk6RtnLKUZnfJEY%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQTSNVWO3556NRZAIY5JCTPUIRE.png&h=031c40a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林本利：當這些紓困措施在立法會申請額外撥款時遇上泛民議員阻撓，更是中正下懷，令受惠的市民對泛民反感，在九月立法會選舉把選票投給建制派議員。<br />\n<br />\n因應經濟衰退，特首林鄭月娥早前推出紓困措施，每年涉及數以百億元經常開支，美其名是紓解民困，實質屬政治舉措，大幅增加政府經常性支出，要下一代年輕人埋單...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200314/TXLZGALR3NTKDIVFN74EG6TRTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200314%2FTXLZGALR3NTKDIVFN74EG6TRTY%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=cf530c93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200314%2FTXLZGALR3NTKDIVFN74EG6TRTY%2F&h=0421ed94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200314/TXLZGALR3NTKDIVFN74EG6TRTY/</a>"},{"pid":"939803d2fa7357e0c464e06bb5472517bd6a4a8d","tid":1924953,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"Dklm"},{"pid":"435dc1cbe6c6c77f0d0f13c206a82a8266d7c51b","tid":1924953,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"邊有下一代<br />\n諗多咗"},{"pid":"9507491478add9b7e37deee641a21539bf18674a","tid":19249